      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test sample characterization must include full hematological profiling of blood analogue or porcine blood used; batch-to-batch variability must be quantified and reported.",
      "rationale": "Test sample factor was not assessed; blood analogue batch characterization data were not available for review. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 2 assigned conservatively; required level 4 not met."
