    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient evidence to support the VAD submission. Monte Carlo UQ was completed and hemolysis predictions fell below the clinical threshold at all assessed operating points. Assurance level Medium reflects the team's judgment that the overall body of evidence is adequate for regulatory submission despite individual factor gaps.",
